Package: alff
Architecture: all
Depends: perl, libxml-simple-perl, gawk, bash
Description: A Linux Firewall Framework - rule generation
 This package is part of the "A Linux Firewall Framework".
 .
 This package contains the tools for managing firewall configuration and
 generating rulesets for your firewalls.

Package: alff-cat
Architecture: all
Depends: iptables
Description: A Linux Firewall Framework - Config Acceptor Tool
 This package is part of the "A Linux Firewall Framework".
 .
 This package contains tools to load new rules to your firewall machines.
 It provides support for easy and automated roll-back if the new ruleset
 does not work as expected.
